FT  22 SEP 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
SHARES in Johannesburg were weaker overall as investors reacted to a
stronger financial rand. The gold index was down 1 at 1,637, the industrial
index shed 11 to 4,490 and the overall index was 4 lower at 3,827.
